  Looping Elements

In this video, I'm going to show you how to you can add life to your static backgrounds by using an amazing tool called Loopflow. This tool allows you to add looping animations in a realistic way. While this tool isn't native to After Effects, I highly recommend checking it out if you're interested in adding in as much life as possible.
